    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理电影放映时间表！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解你的观众，选择在正确的时间放映热门电影！仔细计划放映时间，填满你的放映厅，提高客户满意度。每周选择哪些电影上映完全取决于你；制定好你的策略！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>维护秩序！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可能会有人想要打扰电影院的安宁！识别并干预吸烟者和秘密录制影片的人。要迅速，否则其他顾客可能会因不满而离开。通过掌掴来维护秩序，确保所有顾客都满意！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>爆米花和饮料服务</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有热腾腾的爆米花和冷饮，任何电影院体验都不完整！通过提供最美味的小吃来提高客户满意度。记住，每次服务都能让你更进一步！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建立你的团队，获得成功！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单独管理电影院帝国可能很困难。通过招聘扩大你的团队，提高客户满意度。合适的员工将提升你的服务质量，让你走上巅峰！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
